{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "In scenes with heavy pedestrian occlusion, which poses a significant challenge for pedestrian object detection, [54]proposed a multiscale feature attention fusion network called Parallel Feature Fusion with CBAM (PFF-CB) in 2022.",
    "The PFF-CB module effectively integrates feature information from different scales and uses the Convolutional Block Attention Module (CBAM) to enhance critical feature information in both spatial and channel dimensions.",
    "A parallel feature fusion module based on the Feature Pyramid Network (FPN) is employed to enhance key features.",
    "Reference [55] introduced a YOLO-based method that incorporated softPool into spatial pyramid pooling (SPP) to preserve detailed object information and ensure the inclusion of small targets.",
    "They also utilized depth-wise separable convolution, which requires fewer parameters compared to traditional convolutions, to reduce the model's parameter count."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "In scenes with heavy pedestrian occlusion, which poses a significant challenge for pedestrian object detection, [54]proposed a multiscale feature attention fusion network called Parallel Feature Fusion with CBAM (PFF-CB) in 2022.",
    "Reference [55] introduced a YOLO-based method that incorporated softPool into spatial pyramid pooling (SPP) to preserve detailed object information and ensure the inclusion of small targets."
